                  <item>Bhudda,</item>
                  <item>Ormuzd god of light</item>
                  <item>Ahrimanes god of darkness</item>
                  <item>Parsees from Persia followers of Zoroaster their pope <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">or high priest</add> is called "Mobed"</item>
                  <item>Zoroaster, (Zerdusht)</item>
                  <item>Vishnu preserver of the world</item>
                  <item>image of the Lingam the male sign</item>
                  <item>Fot <add rend="unmarked" place="infralinear">(Phtah)</add> the Chinese god</item>
                  <item>bonze Japanese with a yellow robe</item>
