                  <list><item><del rend="overstrike">Kaldee</del> Kaldee (Sabean Kaldee of Assyria.)</item></list>
                 
                  <milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-full"/>
                  <list>
                     <item>Orus, the sun</item>
                     <item>Serapis, a god of ensemble, I think</item>
                     <item>Hercules</item>
                     <item>Osiris, "to give forms."</item>
                     <item>"I am he who finds nothing more divine than simple and natural things are divine.—"</item>
                     <item>Pluto</item>
                     <item>Satan</item>
                     <item>Lucifer</item>
                     <item>Typhon, (made up of all that opposes hinders, obstructs, revolts.</item>
                     <item>Charon, the ferryman to Tartarus, and to Elysium</item>
                     <item>Rhadamanthus, <add rend="unmarked" place="supralinear">Minos</add> judges of the dead,—the wand, the bend, the ushers, and the urns.</item>
                  </list>
               </note>
