               <note type="authorial" resp="#h1"><list>
               <item>Talmud (of Jerusalem) very old</item>
               <item>"Sybilline verses among the ancients"</item>
               <item>always looking for "a great mediator, a judge, god, <add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">lover,</add> legislator, friend of the poor and degraded, conqueror of powers."</item>
               <item>Krishna, (? thence Christ)</item></list></note>
            </body></floatingText></q>
