         <p><list>
            <item>Sunday ( the sun</item>
            <item>Monday ( moon</item>
            <item>Tuesday ( Tuisco, an ancient Teuton deity</item>
            <item>Wednesday ( Woden, (or Odin)</item>
            <item>Thursday ( Thor—(thunder). "</item>
